Package edu.uiowa.cs.warp

Class Visualization

java.lang.Object
edu.uiowa.cs.warp.Visualization
All Implemented Interfaces:
Visualizable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ChannelVisualization, CommunicationGraphVisualization, ExecutionVisualization, GraphVizVisualization, LatencyVisualization, NotImplentedVisualization, ProgramVisualization, ReliabilityVisualization, ReportVisualization, SensorNetworkVisualization, WorkLoadVisualization
abstract class Visualization extends Object implements Visualizable
Provides default visualizations as an abstract class. Uses GraphStream for enhanced visualizations that include text in the top pane and an animated graph in the bottom pane.
Version:
2.0 Fall 2025
Author:
sgoddard
